"{\"uid\": \"theinertia.com-surf-jack-robinson-olympic-surfing-ocean\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"We are not there with wave pool yet, says the West Oz native.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 61, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo: ISA  It turns out I am not alone in thinking Olympic surfing should not take place in wave pools.In a recent op-ed,I disagreed with two world champions, Gabriel Medina and Filipe Toledo.\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filipe Toledo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filipe Toledo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipe_Toledo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They both clamored for an Olympic wave pool following the 2024 Olympics in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.999999946354366, \"rank\": 5.363974027767567e-08, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many on the internet were quite correctly asking who the hell I thought I was disagreeing with such distinguished surfers.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But thankfully, Jack Robinson has rushed to my aid.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.9386373765639355, \"rank\": 0.06492926756571017, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson was quoted in theSydney Morning Heraldwith a scathing review of wave pools, saying pools \\\"are not great to watch,\\\" \\\"boring\\\" and \\\"repetitive,\\\" and that they completely remove the skill of understanding the ocean from competition.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's the full quote:  \\\"Personally, if an [Olympic] host country has waves, then use them.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"America has waves in Hawaii and California.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999988781930296, \"rank\": 1.0794099512850482e-06, \"text\": \"Hawaii\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.999996210642752, \"rank\": 2.623448047706989e-06, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people might prefer a wave pool because it suits their surfing but to me, working out the ocean is a big part of competitive surfing.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's such a skill and you take that away in a wave pool.\\\"\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And from a spectator point of view, personally I do not think wave pools are great to watch.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe one day they will be.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now, I think it's very repetitive to watch.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly the waves can only handle so much size and if a wave's quite long it gets boring, it's the same maneuvers and moves over and over again.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not writing off wave pools, I think one day they will have their place.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now, for the Olympics, I do not think so.\\\"\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson was one of the surfers most affected by the unpredictable nature of the ocean at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's final he was left stranded for the better part of the heat waiting for a good wave to get back in the running for gold.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the wave never came.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So Robinson coming out against the wave pool idea is a strong counterpunch to the media push by Medina and Toledo.\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.925598837452843e-19, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toledo_Rockets_football\", \"score\": 0.928528552569206, \"rank\": 0.0417290580645165, \"text\": \"Toledo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toledo_Rockets_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toledo_Rockets_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson and I align on another key pointI got into during my opinion piece.It's not that wave pools will never be the answer.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the pool technology that exists right now and the runway of Los Angeles in 2028 and Brisbane in 2032, there is not a need to drydock the Olympic surfing event on land.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999997650702702, \"rank\": 1.3788781148742236e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2133, \"end\": 2141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9998914096807872, \"rank\": 0.00010056764161714978, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One day pool technology will get to that point.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or maybe in 2036 the Olympics will be held in a landlocked country.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But coming off the back of the excitement and success of Teahupo'o, now's not the time to switch up the winning formula of ocean surfing.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson endorses this logic.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2471, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.8493428570218489, \"rank\": 0.15911980792066605, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the best.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We promise.\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join our community of contributors.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Inertia is part ofAllGear Digital'sportfolio of media brands.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}]}"